                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The unit draws bolas and hurls them in a @Template[type:cone|distance:15], inflicting @Damage[3d6[bludgeoning]|traits:nonlethal]{3d6 nonlethal bludgeoning} to creatures in the area (@Check[reflex|dc:21|basic] save). Any creature who critically fails its save is also knocked @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Prone] and takes an additional @Damage[1d4[bludgeoning]|traits:nonlethal]{1d4 nonlethal bludgeoning} damage.</p>"
